title: Kitty Cleveland - Sacred Christmas Songs
description:
Kitty Cleveland - Sacred Christmas Songs

In these traditional holiday selections from her Christmas collection "O Holy Night", Kitty Cleveland moves us with beautiful arrangements that will help draw us into the Christmas spirit. For over twenty years, Kitty has been inspiring audiences with her classically-trained angelic vocals. This CD also includes an excerpt from her stirring testimony of her own conversion.

Song Titles:

1. O Little Town of Bethlehem
2. The First Noel
3. Away in a Manger
4. What Child is this?
5. O Holy Night
6. Silent Night
7. We Three Kings
8. Ave Maria
